OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784128711
OL,3,CWoman charged with aggravated arson
OL,4,Cover moorland fire
OL,6,FA 20-year-old woman has been charged
OL,7,Fwith aggravated arson after a massive
OL,8,Fmoorland fire was declared a major
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FShania Care-Slede, of Market Street,
OL,12,FHyde, has been charged with aggravated
OL,13,Farson, being reckless as to whether
OL,14,Flife was endangered, and dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving.
OL,17,FCrews from Greater Manchester Fire and
OL,18,FRescue Service (GMFRS) were called to
OL,19,Fthe hills close to Dovestone Reservoir
OL,20,Fin Greenfield, Oldham, shortly before
OL,21,F8.40pm on Satuday, 11 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
