FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784128711
OL,3,CWoman charged with aggravated arson
OL,4,Cover moorland fire
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) have
OL,7,Fconfirmed Cara-Slede has been remanded
OL,8,Fin custody and is due to appear at
OL,9,FManchester Magistrates' Court on
OL,10,FTuesday, 14 July.
OL,12,FWhile officials have not yet formally
OL,13,Fconfirmed the cause of the blaze,
OL,14,Fvideos circulating on social media
OL,15,Fappear to show a group of people
OL,16,Fsetting off fireworks in the area
OL,17,Fshortly before the fire took hold.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784128711
OL,3,CWoman charged with aggravated arson
OL,4,Cover moorland fire
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Andrew Day said:
OL,7,F"While we have secured charges against
OL,8,Fone individual, our investigation
OL,9,Fremains ongoing. Detectives are
OL,10,Fcarefully reviewing all available
OL,11,Fevidence to identify anyone else who
OL,12,Fmay have been involved in criminality
OL,13,Flinked to this incident.
OL,15,F"We're committed to pursuing all those
OL,16,Fresponsible. Anyone identified as
OL,17,Fhaving committed a criminal offence
OL,18,Fcan expect to be robustly dealt with.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
