OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784128711
OL,3,CWoman charged with aggravated arson
OL,4,Cover moorland fire
OL,6,F"I would also like to thank the public
OL,7,Ffor the support they have shown so far
OL,8,Fand encourage anyone with information
OL,9,For footage that may assist our
OL,10,Fenquiries to come forward."
OL,12,FCrews remain at the site on 14 July,
OL,13,Fworking to extinguish remaining
OL,14,Fhotspots and monitor the area.
OL,16,FThe major incident comes just over 24
OL,17,Fhours after the death of a teenage boy
OL,18,Fat Dovestone Reservoir.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
